headline: FedEx ‘highly confident’ grounded MD-11s will return to service
summary: FedEx continues to show strong optimism that it will soon begin operating its fleet of MD-11 freighters despite no signs from regulators investigating the deadly UPS accident about when they’ll lift the aircraft’s flight ban.
